<section sectnbr = "4A">
<servcat sctnbr = "04" scnbr = "01">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70B4106011" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "1">
<title>
Brake Light Switch Inspection
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4106011001">
<title>
Continuity Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70B4106010">Brake Light Switch Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Check brake light switch for continuity between terminals at each shaft condition.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If check result is not as specified, replace switch.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A410014.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.573mm" ver = "01" gw = "208" gh = "116"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8C50A410013.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "28.013mm" ver = "01" gw = "188" gh = "62"/>
</figure>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B4106011002">
<title>
Lighting Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
Depress the brake pedal until brake light turns on and measure the brake pedal stroke to that point.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If the pedal stroke is not as specified, remove and reinstall brake light switch.
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Brake pedal stroke until brake light turns on “a”
</title>
<ptxt>
LHD: 5.87 – 15.48 mm (0.23 – 0.61 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
RHD: 6.39 – 15.98 mm (0.25 – 0.63 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B410015.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.048mm" ver = "01" gw = "60" gh = "117"/>
</figure>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
